p, optionally add display conditions, and publish.'=>'继续审核您的订单附加项，可选择添加显示条件并发布。','You must select an offer product.'=>'您必须选择一个优惠产品。','Offer'=>'优惠','Auto Add Order Bump to Cart'=>'自动将订单附加项添加到购物车','If conditions are satisfied, automatically add this order bump to the cart. Useful for free gifts or other offers that don\\\'t require customer action.'=>'如果满足条件，自动将此订单附加项添加到购物车。适用于免费赠品或其他不需要客户操作的优惠。','Auto Match Variations Between Search and Offer Product'=>'自动匹配搜索产品与优惠产品的变体','Add offer product to the cart with the same variable configuration as the product below.'=>'将优惠产品以与以下产品相同的变量配置添加到购物车。','Only applies when Auto Match Cart Product and Offer Product are variable products with matching variation attributes (Size, Color, etc)'=>'仅当自动匹配购物车产品和优惠产品都是具有匹配变体属性（尺寸、颜色等）的变量产品时适用','Leave unchecked to have customers to select variation options in a modal window.'=>'未选中时，客户需在弹窗中选择变体选项。','If offer product is not variable, this option is ignored.'=>'如果优惠产品不是变量产品，则忽略此选项。','Auto Match Variations Cart Product'=>'自动匹配购物车产品变体','The product in the cart to match the Order Bump variations to.'=>'购物车中用于匹配订单附加项变体的产品。','Match Quantity of Offer Product to Display Condition Product'=>'匹配优惠产品数量与显示条件产品数量','If customer has two of the display condition product in the cart, two of the offer product will be added to the cart.'=>'如果客户购物车中有两个显示条件产品，则会添加两个优惠产品到购物车。','Match Quantity Cart Product'=>'匹配购物车产品数量','The product in the cart to match the Order Bump quantity to.'=>'购物车中用于匹配订单附加项数量的产品。','Quantity of Offer Product To Add'=>'要添加的优惠产品数量','The quantity to add to the cart when offer is accepted.'=>'接受优惠时添加到购物车的数量。','Allow Customer To Change Quantity In Cart'=>'允许客户在购物车中更改数量','Allow customer to change the quantity of this order bump in the cart.'=>'允许客户更改购物车中此订单附加项的数量。','Offer Language'=>'优惠语言','After Checkout Submit Modal Heading'=>'结账提交后弹窗标题','Default if blank: Your order is almost complete...'=>'为空时默认：您的订单即将完成...','After Checkout Submit Modal Subheading'=>'结账提交后弹窗副标题','Default if blank: Add this offer