推荐）','Enabled'=>'启用','Link each cart item to product page.'=>'将每个购物车商品链接到产品页面。','Open in New Window'=>'新窗口打开','Open cart item links in a new window.'=>'在新窗口打开购物车商品链接。','Cart Item Data Display'=>'购物车商品数据展示','Choose how to display cart item data.'=>'选择如何展示购物车商品数据。','Short (Recommended)'=>'简短（推荐）','Display only variation values. For example, Size: XL, Color: Red is displayed as XL / Red. (Recommended)'=>'仅显示变体值。例如，尺寸：XL，颜色：红色显示为 XL / 红色。（推荐）','WooCommerce Default'=>'WooCommerce 默认','Each variation is displayed on a separate line using this format: Label: Value'=>'每个变体单独一行显示，格式为：标签：值','Store Policies'=>'商店政策','Store Policies are displayed as links in the footer of the checkout, order pay, and thank you pages. Clicking them displays the policy in a modal window.'=>'商店政策作为链接显示在结账、订单支付和感谢页面的页脚。点击链接将在模态窗口中显示政策内容。','Control the Order Received / Thank You endpoint.'=>'控制“订单已接收 / 谢谢您”端点。','Enable Thank You Page Template'=>'启用感谢页面模板','Enable thank you page / order received template.'=>'启用感谢页面 / 订单已接收模板。','Enable Map Embed'=>'启用地图嵌入','Enable or disable Google Maps embed on Thank You page. Requires Google API key.'=>'启用或禁用感谢页面上的谷歌地图嵌入。需要谷歌API密钥。','Enable Thank You Page Template For Viewing Orders in My Account'=>'启用“我的账户”中查看订单的感谢页面模板','When checked, viewing orders in My Account will use the Thank You page template.'=>'选中后，“我的账户”中查看订单将使用感谢页面模板。','Order Statuses'=>'订单状态','Choose which Order Statuses are shown as a progress bar on the Thank You page.'=>'选择哪些订单状态在感谢页面上显示为进度条。','Icon Color'=>'图标颜色','Heading above the suggested products. Leave blank for default. Default: You may also like&hellip;'=>'推荐产品上方的标题。留空为默认。默认值：您可能还喜欢&hellip;','You may also like…'=>'您可能还喜欢…','Enable Random Cross Sells Fallback'=>'启用随机交叉销售备选','If none of the cart products have cross sell items defined, display random products instead.'=>'如果购物车中的商品没有定义交叉销售商品，则显示随机商品。','Enable Floating Cart Button'=>'启用浮动购物车按钮','Enable floating cart button on the bottom right of pages.'=>'在页面右下角启用浮动购物车按钮。','Right Position'=>'右侧位置','The position from the right side of the screen in pixels. Default: 20'=>'距离屏幕右侧的像素位置。默认值：20','Bottom Position'=>'底部位置','The position from the bottom of the screen in pixels. Default: 20'=>'距离屏幕底部的像素位置。默认值：20','Hide Button If Empty Cart'=>'购物车为空时隐藏按钮','Hide floating cart button if cart is empty.'=>'购物车为空时隐藏浮动购物车按钮。','Free Shipping Progress Bar'=>'免运费进度条','Configure the Free Shipping Progress Bar'=>'配置免运费进度条','Enable Free Shipping Progress Bar'=>'启用免运费进度条','Enable Free Shipping progress bar to show customers how close they are to obtaining free shipping. Uses your shipping settings to determine limits. To override, specify amount below.'=>'启用免运费进度条，向客户显示他们距离获得免运费还有多近。使用您的运费设置确定限制。要覆盖，请在下方指定金额。','Free Shipping Threshold'=>'免运费门槛','Cart subtotal required to qualify for free shipping. To use automatic detection based on shipping configuration, leave blank. Enter in store base currency.'=>'达到免运费资格所需的购物车小计。要使用基于运费配置的自动检测，请留空。以商店基础货币输入。','Amount Remaining Message'=>'剩余金额消息','You\'re %s away from free shipping!'=>'你离免费送货还有%s步!','The amount remaining to qualify for free shipping message. Leave blank for default. Default: You\'re %s away from free shipping!'=>'达到免费送货资格所需的剩余金额消息。留空则使用默认。默认：您还差 %s 即可享受免费送货！','Please ensure your amount remaining message includes the %s placeholder which is replaced with amount remaining when displayed to customers.'=>'请确保您的剩余金额消息包含 %s 占位符，该占位符在显示给客户时会被剩余金额替换。','Free Shipping Message'=>'免费送货消息','The free shipping message. Leave blank for default. Default: Congrats! You get free standard shipping.'=>'免费送货消息。留空则使用默认。默认：恭喜！您获得免费标准送货。','Enable Free Shipping Progress Bar At Checkout'=>'在结账时启用免费送货进度条','Enable Free Shipping Progress Bar on the checkout page cart summary.'=>'在结账页面的购物车摘要中启用免费送货进度条。','Progress Indicator Color'=>'进度指示颜色','Progress Bar Background Color'=>'进度条背景颜色','Options'=>'选项','Control various Side Cart options.'=>'控制各种侧边购物车选项。','Disable Cart Auto Open'=>'禁用购物车自动打开','Instead of opening the side cart, gently shake the floating cart button (if visible) to indicate a successful add to cart event.'=>'不打开侧边购物车，而是轻轻摇动浮动购物车按钮（如果可见）以表示成功添加到购物车事件。','Enable AJAX Add to Cart'=>'启用 AJAX 添加到购物车','Use AJAX on archive and single product pages to add items to cart. By default, WooCommerce requires a full form submit with page reload. Enabling this option uses AJAX to add items to the cart.'=>'在归档和单个产品页面使用 AJAX 添加商品到购物车。默认情况下，WooCommerce 需要完整的表单提交并重新加载页面。启用此选项后，使用 AJAX 添加商品到购物车。','Enable Express Payment Buttons'=>'启用快捷支付按钮','Enable express payment buttons from gateways that support the WooCommerce Minicart.'=>'启用支持 WooCommerce 迷你购物车的支付网关的快捷支付按钮。','Enable order bumps that are set to display below cart items to appear in side cart.'=>'启用设置为显示在购物车商品下方的订单附加销售，使其出现在侧边购物车中。','Allow Variation Changes'=>'允许变体更改','Displays an edit link under cart items that allows customers to change which variation is selected in the cart.'=>'在购物车商品下显示编辑链接，允许客户更改购物车中选择的变体。','Enable sale price under on cart item labels in side cart. Example: <s>$10.00</s> $5.00'=>'在侧边购物车的购物车商品标签下启用促销价显示。例如：<s>$10.00</s> $5.00','Enable Coupons'=>'启用优惠券','Enable customers to apply coupons from the side cart.'=>'允许客户从侧边购物车应用优惠券。','Hide Coupon Code Field Behind Link'=>'通过链接隐藏优惠券代码字段','Initially hide coupon field until "Have a coupon code?" link is clicked.'=>'初始隐藏优惠券字段，直到点击“有优惠券代码？”链接。','Show Shipping and Totals'=>'显示运费和总计','Enable customers to see shipping and order total in addition to subtotal.'=>'允许客户查看运费和订单总计，除了小计之外。','Enable Continue Shopping Button'=>'启用继续购物按钮','Enable Continue Shopping Button at bottom of Side Cart. Disabled by default.'=>'在侧边购物车底部启用继续购物按钮。默认禁用。','You probably do not want to select any pickup methods here. If you do not select any Local Pickup Shipping Methods, we will add an ad-hoc local pickup shipping method in each zone for you. If you would prefer to manage this yourself, you can select the methods you want to use here.'=>'您可能不想在这里选择任何自提方式。如果您未选择任何本地自提配送方式，我们将在每个区域为您添加一个临时本地自提配送方式。如果您希望自行管理，可以在这里选择您想使用的方式。','Reasons You Might Want To Specify Your Own Pickup Methods:'=>'您可能想指定自提方式的原因：','You are charging for local pickup.'=>'您对本地自提收费。','You want to use a custom local pickup method name.'=>'您想使用自定义的本地自提方式名称。','You have multiple local pickup options. (Not to be confused with locations. You should not use multiple local pickup methods for locations.)'=>'您有多个本地自提选项。（不要与地点混淆。您不应为地点使用多个本地自提方式。）','Other Shipping Method'=>'其他运输方式','Enter the name of your local pickup shipping method. If you have multiple options, or the name varies, check the box below to use regular expressions.'=>'输入您的本地自提运输方式名称。如果您有多个选项，或名称有所不同，请勾选下面的框以使用正则表达式。','Enable Regex'=>'启用正则表达式','Match local shipping method name with regex.'=>'使用正则表达式匹配本地运输方式名称。','Configure Cloudflare Turnstile CAPTCHA protection for your checkout and account pages.'=>'为您的结账和账户页面配置 Cloudflare Turnstile CAPTCHA 保护。','Enable Cloudflare Turnstile'=>'启用 Cloudflare Turnstile','Enable Cloudflare Turnstile CAPTCHA protection'=>'启用 Cloudflare Turnstile CAPTCHA 保护','Site Key'=>'站点密钥','Your Cloudflare Turnstile site key'=>'您的 Cloudflare Turnstile 站点密钥','Secret Key'=>'密钥','Your Cloudflare Turnstile secret key'=>'您的 Cloudflare Turnstile 密钥','Enable on Checkout'=>'结账时启用','Show Turnstile on the checkout page'=>'在结账页面显示 Turnstile','Enable on Order Pay'=>'订单支付时启用','Show Turnstile on the order pay page'=>'在订单支付页面显示 Turnstile','Enable on Login'=>'登录时启用','Show Turnstile on the My Account login form'=>'在我的账户登录表单显示 Turnstile','Enable on Registration'=>'注册时启用','Show Turnstile on the My Account registration form'=>'在我的账户注册表单显示 Turnstile','Position on Checkout'=>'结账位置','Where to display the Turnstile widget on checkout'=>'在结账页面显示 Turnstile 小部件的位置','Before Place Order Button'=>'下单按钮前','Display just before the place order button'=>'显示在下单按钮之前','Before Payment Methods'=>'支付方式前','Display before payment method selection'=>'显示在支付方式选择之前','After Payment Methods'=>'支付方式后','Display after payment method selection'=>'显示在支付方式选择之后','Theme'=>'主题','Visual theme for the Turnstile widget'=>'Turnstile 小部件的视觉主题','Light'=>'浅色','Light theme'=>'浅色主题','Dark'=>'深色','Dark theme'=>'深色主题','Auto'=>'自动','Automatic based on user preference'=>'根据用户偏好自动选择','Size'=>'大小','Size of the Turnstile widget'=>'Turnstile 小部件的大小','Normal'=>'正常','Standard size widget'=>'标准大小小部件','Compact'=>'紧凑','Smaller widget size'=>'较小的小部件大小','Guest Users Only'=>'仅限访客用户','Only show Turnstile for guest (non-logged-in) users'=>'仅对访客（未登录用户）显示 Turnstile','Google API'=>'Google API','Used for the maps embed on the thank you page as well as Google Address Autocomplete.'=>'用于感谢页面的地图嵌入以及 Google 地址自动完成。','Google API Key'=>'Google API 密钥','Used by Address Autocomplete and Thank You Page Maps Embed.'=>'由地址自动完成和感谢页面地图嵌入使用。','Themes and Plugins'=>'主题和插件','Integrations with 3rd party themes and plugins.'=>'与第三方主题和插件的集成。','Control express checkout options.'=>'控制快捷结账选项。','Disable Express Checkout'=>'禁用快捷结账','Prevent Express Checkout options from loading, such as Apple Pay and PayPal. <a href="https://www.checkoutwc.com/documentation/supported-express-payment-gateways/" target="_blank" class="ml-1 text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">Learn More</a>'=>'阻止快捷结账选项加载，例如 Apple Pay 和 PayPal。 <a href="https://www.checkoutwc.com/documentation/supported-express-payment-gateways/" target="_blank" class="ml-1 text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">了解更多</a>','Detected Gateways'=>'检测到的网关','Gateway'=>'网关','Express Checkout Support'=>'快捷结账支持','Recommendation'=>'推荐','No supported gateways detected. <a class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800" target="_blank" href="https://www.checkoutwc.com/documentation/supported-express-payment-gateways/">See our recommended Express Checkout gateways here.</a>'=>'未检测到支持的网关。 <a class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800" target="_blank" href="https://www.checkoutwc.com/documentation/supported-express-payment-gateways/">请查看我们推荐的快捷结账网关。</a>','Steps'=>'步骤','Control the checkout steps.'=>'控制结账步骤。','Disable Cart Step'=>'禁用购物车步骤','Disable to skip the cart and redirect customers directly to checkout after adding a product to the cart. (Incompatible with Side Cart)'=>'禁用后，添加产品到购物车后将跳过购物车，直接重定向客户到结账页面。（与侧边购物车不兼容）','Disable Shipping Step'=>'禁用运输步骤','Disable to hide the shipping method step. Useful if you only have one shipping option for all orders.'=>'禁用后隐藏运输方式步骤。如果您所有订单只有一种运输选项，此功能非常有用。','Enable Order Review Step'=>'启用订单审核步骤','Adds a review step after payment information before finalizing order. Useful for jurisdictions which require additional confirmation before order submission. (Cannot be used with One Page Checkout)'=>'在付款信息后、订单最终确认前添加审核步骤。适用于需要额外确认才能提交订单的司法管辖区。（不能与单页结账同时使用）','Enable One Page Checkout'=>'启用单页结账','Show all checkout steps on  one page. Useful for digital stores. (Cannot be used with Order Review Step)'=>'在一页上显示所有结账步骤。适用于数字商店。（不能与订单审核步骤同时使用）','Shipping Options'=>'运输选项','Control shipping options.'=>'控制运输选项。','Auto Select Free Shipping Method (if available)'=>'自动选择免费运输方式（如果可用）','WooCommerce has a habit of not selecting the free shipping method if it is setup to be conditionally enabled. This option auto-selects the free shipping on page load.'=>'WooCommerce 通常不会选择条件启用的免费运输方式。此选项在页面加载时自动选择免费运输。','Login and Registration'=>'登录和注册','Control how login and registration function on your checkout page.'=>'控制结账页面上的登录和注册功能。','Disable Automatic Login Modal'=>'禁用自动登录弹窗','Normally the login modal automatically opens if the entered email address matches an existing account. This disables that behavior.'=>'通常如果输入的邮箱地址匹配现有账户，登录弹窗会自动打开。此选项禁用该行为。','Registration'=>'注册','Choose how customers obtain a password when registering an account.'=>'选择客户注册账户时如何获取密码。','Enhanced (Recommended)'=>'增强（推荐）','Automatically generate a username and password and email it to the customer using the native WooCommerce functionality. (Recommended)'=>'自动生成用户名和密码，并通过 WooCommerce 原生功能发送邮件给客户。（推荐）','A password field is provided for the customer to select their own password. Not recommended.'=>'为客户提供密码字段以自行选择密码。不推荐。','User Matching'=>'用户匹配','Choose how to handle guest orders and accounts.'=>'选择如何处理访客订单和账户。','Enabled (Recommended)'=>'启用（推荐）','Automatically matches guest orders to user accounts on new purchase as well as on registration of a new user. (Recommended)'=>'自动将访客订单匹配到用户账户，适用于新购买和新用户注册。（推荐）','Guest orders will not be linked to matching accounts.'=>'访客订单不会链接到匹配的账户。','Field Options'=>'字段选项','Control how different checkout fields appear.'=>'控制不同结账字段的显示方式。','Phone Field'=>'电话字段','Determines whether the WooCommerce native phone field is enabled.'=>'决定是否启用 WooCommerce 原生电话字段。','Hidden'=>'隐藏','Optional'=>'可选','Required'=>'必填','Enable Order Notes Field'=>'启用订单备注字段','Enable or disable WooCommerce Order Notes field. (Default: Disabled)'=>'启用或禁用 WooCommerce 订单备注字段。（默认：禁用）','Order Notes field is being controlled by a filter or a plugin.'=>'订单备注字段由过滤器或插件控制。','Hide Optional Address Fields Behind Links'=>'将可选地址字段隐藏在链接后面','Recommended to increase conversions. Example link text: Add Company (optional)'=>'建议增加转化率。示例链接文本：添加公司（可选）','Disable Email Domain Autocomplete'=>'禁用电子邮件域自动完成','Disable email domain autocomplete.'=>'禁用电子邮件域自动完成。','Enable Separate House Number and Street Name Address Fields'=>'启用单独的门牌号和街道名称地址字段','Values are combined into a single address_1 field based on country selected by customer.'=>'根据客户选择的国家，值会合并到单个 address_1 字段中。','Separate Address Fields Display Order'=>'单独地址字段显示顺序','Choose how display separate address 1 fields.'=>'选择如何显示单独的地址 1 字段。','[House Number] [Street Name]'=>'[门牌号] [街道名称]','Display the House Number before the Street Name. (Default)'=>'门牌号显示在街道名称之前。（默认）','[Street Name] [House Number]'=>'[街道名称] [门牌号]','Display the Street Name before the House Number.'=>'街道名称显示在门牌号之前。','Separate Address Fields is incompatible with Google Address Autocomplete. <a target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 underline" href="https://www.checkoutwc.com/documentation/google-address-autocomplete-and-discreet-house-number-and-street-name-address-fields/">Learn More</a>'=>'单独地址字段与谷歌地址自动完成功能不兼容。 <a target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 underline" href="https://www.checkoutwc.com/documentation/google-address-autocomplete-and-discreet-house-number-and-street-name-address-fields/">了解更多</a>','Enable Full Name Field'=>'启用全名字段','Enable to replace first and last name fields with a single full name field.'=>'启用后，用单个全名字段替换名字和姓氏字段。','Enable Highlighted Countries'=>'启用高亮国家','Promote selected countries to the top of the countries list in country dropdowns.'=>'将选定的国家提升到国家下拉列表的顶部。','Highlighted Countries'=>'高亮国家','The countries to show first in country dropdowns.'=>'在国家下拉列表中优先显示的国家。','Enable International Phone Field'=>'启用国际电话字段','Validate phone number entry based on selected country. Replaces phone field placeholder with example phone number. Stores phone number according to International Phone Format.'=>'根据所选国家验证电话号码输入。用示例电话号码替换电话字段占位符。根据国际电话格式存储电话号码。','International Phone Format'=>'国际电话格式','Choose how to store phone numbers.'=>'选择如何存储电话号码。','Raw Value (No Formatting)'=>'原始值（无格式）','The number is stored exactly how the user entered it.'=>'号码按用户输入的原样存储。','E164'=>'E164','Format phone number with E164 standard.'=>'使用 E164 标准格式化电话号码。','International'=>'国际格式','Format phone number with RFC3966 standard without the tel: prefix'=>'使用 RFC3966 标准格式化电话号码，不带 tel: 前缀','National'=>'国家格式','Format phone number based on selected country. US Example (555) 555 - 5555, UK Example: 07911 123457'=>'根据所选国家格式化电话号码。美国示例 (555) 555 - 5555，英国示例：07911 123457','RFC3966'=>'RFC3966','Format phone number with RFC3966 standard.'=>'使用 RFC3966 标准格式化电话号码。','Address Options'=>'地址选项','Control address fields.'=>'控制地址字段。','Force Different Billing Address'=>'强制不同的账单地址','Remove option to use shipping address as billing address.'=>'移除使用送货地址作为账单地址的选项。','Hide Billing Address For Free Orders'=>'免费订单隐藏账单地址','Remove the billing address fields from checkout for free orders.'=>'免费订单结账时移除账单地址字段。','Enabled Billing Address Fields'=>'启用的账单地址字段','Choose which billing address fields are visible for customers.'=>'选择哪些账单地址字段对客户可见。','First Name'=>'名字','Last Name'=>'姓氏','Address 1'=>'地址 1','Address 2'=>'地址 2','Company'=>'公司','Country'=>'国家','Postcode'=>'邮政编码','State'=>'州','City'=>'城市','Disabling the country or state field causes issues with some gateways. Consider leaving these fields enabled.'=>'禁用国家或州字段会导致某些支付网关出现问题。建议保持这些字段启用。','Address Completion and Validation'=>'地址补全与验证','Control some mobile only checkout behaviors.'=>'控制一些仅限移动端的结账行为。','Enable Google Address Autocomplete'=>'启用谷歌地址自动完成','Google Address Autocomplete cannot be used with Separate Address Fields. <a target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 underline" href="https://www.checkoutwc.com/documentation/google-address-autocomplete-and-discreet-house-number-and-street-name-address-fields/">Learn More</a>'=>'谷歌地址自动完成无法与分离地址字段同时使用。<a target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 underline" href="https://www.checkoutwc.com/documentation/google-address-autocomplete-and-discreet-house-number-and-street-name-address-fields/">了解更多</a>','Enable Fetchify Address Autocomplete'=>'启用 Fetchify 地址自动完成','Enable or disable Fetchify address autocomplete feature. <a href="https://fetchify.com" class="text-blue-600 underline" target="_blank">Requires Fetchify access token.</a>'=>'启用或禁用 Fetchify 地址自动完成功能。<a href="https://fetchify.com" class="text-blue-600 underline" target="_blank">需要 Fetchify 访问令牌。</a>','Fetchify Access Token'=>'Fetchify 访问令牌','Your Fetchify access token.'=>'您的 Fetchify 访问令牌。','You can only use one address autocomplete service at a time. Please disable one of the services.'=>'您一次只能使用一个地址自动完成服务。请禁用其中一个服务。','Enable Smarty Address Validation'=>'启用 Smarty 地址验证','Validates shipping address with Smarty.com and provides alternative, corrected addresses for incorrect or incomplete addresses.'=>'使用 Smarty.com 验证送货地址，并为错误或不完整的地址提供替代的、更正的地址。','Smarty Auth ID'=>'Smarty 认证 ID','Smarty Auth ID. Available in your <a target="_blank" href="https://www.smarty.com/account/keys" class="text-blue-600 underline">Smarty Account</a>'=>'Smarty 认证 ID。可在您的 <a target="_blank" href="https://www.smarty.com/account/keys" class="text-blue-600 underline">Smarty 账户</a> 中获取','Smarty Auth Token'=>'Smarty 认证令牌','Smarty Auth Token. Available in your <a target="_blank" href="https://www.smarty.com/account/keys" class="text-blue-600 underline">Smarty Account</a>.'=>'Smarty 认证令牌。可在您的 <a target="_blank" href="https://www.smarty.com/account/keys" class="text-blue-600 underline">Smarty 账户</a> 中获取。','Enable Cart Editing At Checkout'=>'启用结账时编辑购物车','Enable or disable Cart Editing. Allows customer to remove or adjust quantity of cart items at checkout.'=>'启用或禁用购物车编辑。允许客户在结账时移除或调整购物车商品数量。','Show Item Remove Button'=>'显示商品移除按钮','When hovering over an item, show a button (X) to remove the item.'=>'当鼠标悬停在商品上时，显示一个按钮（X）以移除该商品。','Cart Editing Empty Cart Redirect'=>'购物车编辑空购物车重定向','URL to redirect to when customer empties cart from checkout page. If left blank, customer will be redirected to the cart page.'=>'客户从结账页面清空购物车时重定向的 URL。如果留空，客户将被重定向到购物车页面。','Enable Sticky Cart Summary'=>'启用粘性购物车摘要','If cart summary is shorter than the rest of the content, it will stick to the top of the screen when scrolling.'=>'如果购物车摘要比其他内容短，滚动时它将固定在屏幕顶部。','Mobile Options'=>'移动端选项','Control mobile specific features.'=>'控制移动端特定功能。','Enable Mobile Cart Summary'=>'启用移动购物车摘要','Shows the cart, promo field, and totals at the bottom of the first checkout step.'=>'在第一个结账步骤底部显示购物车、促销字段和总计。','Enable Mobile Totals'=>'启用移动总计','Shows cart totals right above the place order button on mobile.'=>'在移动设备上，在下单按钮正上方显示购物车总计。','Enable Mobile Coupon Field'=>'启用移动优惠券字段','Show coupon field above payment gateways on mobile devices. Helps customers find the coupon field without expanding the cart summary.'=>'在移动设备上，在支付网关上方显示优惠券字段。帮助客户无需展开购物车摘要即可找到优惠券字段。','Enable Mobile Cart Summary is not compatible with Enable Mobile Coupon Field. Please disable one of the options.'=>'启用移动购物车摘要与启用移动优惠券字段不兼容。请禁用其中一个选项。','Enable Mobile Credit Card Logos'=>'启用移动信用卡标志','Show the credit card logos on mobile. Note: Many gateway logos cannot be rendered properly on mobile. It is recommended you test before enabling. Default: Off'=>'在移动设备上显示信用卡标志。注意：许多网关标志无法在移动设备上正确渲染。建议启用前进行测试。默认：关闭','Cart Summary Mobile Label'=>'购物车摘要移动标签','Example: Show order summary and coupons. If left blank, this default will be used: Show order summary'=>'示例：显示订单摘要和优惠券。如果留空，将使用此默认值：显示订单摘要','Order Pay'=>'订单支付','Enable CheckoutWC template for the Order Pay / Customer Payment Page endpoint.'=>'为订单支付/客户付款页面端点启用CheckoutWC模板。','Enable Order Pay Page'=>'启用订单支付页面','Use CheckoutWC templates for Order Pay page.'=>'为订单支付页面使用CheckoutWC模板。','General Template Settings'=>'通用模板设置','Configure your template.'=>'配置您的模板。','Logo'=>'标志','Choose the logo you wish to display in the header. If you do not choose a logo we will use your site name.'=>'选择您希望在页眉中显示的标志。如果未选择标志，我们将使用您的站点名称。','Field Label Style'=>'字段标签样式','Choose how you want form labels styled.'=>'选择您希望表单标签的样式。','Floating (Recommended)'=>'浮动（推荐）','Automatically show and hide labels based on whether the field has a value. (Recommended)'=>'根据字段是否有值自动显示和隐藏标签。（推荐）','Labels appear above each field at all times.'=>'标签始终显示在每个字段上方。','Typography'=>'排版','Configure fonts.'=>'配置字体。','Body Font'=>'正文字体','Choose the font for the body text.'=>'选择正文文本的字体。','Heading Font'=>'标题字体','Choose the font for the headings.'=>'选择标题的字体。','Colors'=>'颜色','Configure template colors.'=>'配置模板颜色。','CSS'=>'CSS','Customize template CSS.'=>'自定义模板CSS。','Custom CSS'=>'自定义CSS','Add Custom CSS rules to fully control the appearance of the checkout template.'=>'添加自定义CSS规则以完全控制结账模板的外观。','Experimental Options'=>'实验性选项','These options are not fully supported and may require a developer to implement successfully.'=>'这些选项尚未完全支持，可能需要开发人员成功实现。','Template Loader'=>'模板加载器','Choose how to load the templates. (Checkout, Order Pay, Thank You)'=>'选择如何加载模板。（结账，订单支付，感谢页）','Distraction Free Portal (Recommended)'=>'无干扰门户（推荐）','Display CheckoutWC templates in a distraction free portal which does not load the active WordPress theme or styles. (Recommended)'=>'在无干扰门户中显示CheckoutWC模板，该门户不会加载活动的WordPress主题或样式。（推荐）','WordPress Theme'=>'WordPress主题','Load CheckoutWC templates within active WordPress theme content area. (<span style="color:red">Unsupported Configuration</span>)'=>'在活动的WordPress主题内容区域内加载CheckoutWC模板。(<span style="color:red">不支持的配置</span>)','Using this option renders our templates inside of your theme content area. This may cause conflicts with your theme\'s stylesheets and scripts. Please note, resolving any issues that arise from this loader will be your responsibility.'=>'使用此选项将在您的主题内容区域内呈现我们的模板。这可能会导致与您的主题样式表和脚本发生冲突。请注意，解决由此加载器引起的任何问题将由您自行负责。','Enable Beta Version Updates'=>'启用测试版更新','Allows automatic updates to the latest beta version.'=>'允许自动更新到最新的测试版。','Delete Plugin Data on Uninstall'=>'卸载时删除插件数据','If you want a fresh start.'=>'如果您想重新开始。','We are great at categorizing things!'=>'我们擅长分类！','Hide Admin Menu Bar Button'=>'隐藏管理员菜单栏按钮','Hide the CheckoutWC admin menu bar button unless you are on the checkout page, or one of the checkout endpoints such as thank you and order pay.'=>'除非您在结账页面或结账端点（如感谢页和订单支付页），否则隐藏 CheckoutWC 管理菜单栏按钮。','Enable Debug Log'=>'启用调试日志','Logs debug information to WP Admin > WooCommerce > Status > Logs > checkout-wc-*.log'=>'将调试信息记录到 WP 管理 > WooCommerce > 状态 > 日志 > checkout-wc-*.log','Enable Usage Tracking'=>'启用使用跟踪','Allow CheckoutWC to track plugin usage.'=>'允许 CheckoutWC 跟踪插件使用情况。','Global'=>'全局','Add custom scripts that run on all enabled CheckoutWC templates. (Checkout, Thank You, Order Pay)'=>'添加在所有启用的 CheckoutWC 模板（结账、感谢、订单支付）上运行的自定义脚本。','Header Scripts'=>'头部脚本','This code will output immediately before the closing <code>&lt;/head&gt;</code> tag in the document source.'=>'此代码将在文档源代码中关闭 <code>&lt;/head&gt;</code> 标签之前立即输出。','Footer Scripts'=>'底部脚本','This code will output immediately before the closing <code>&lt;/body&gt;</code> tag in the document source.'=>'此代码将在文档源代码中关闭 <code>&lt;/body&gt;</code> 标签之前立即输出。','Header and Footer Scripts are HTML only. For PHP, use PHP Snippets option.'=>'头部和底部脚本仅支持 HTML。PHP 请使用 PHP 代码片段选项。','PHP Snippets'=>'PHP 代码片段','Add PHP snippets to modify your checkout page here. If you have lots of snippets, you may want to consider using <a class="text-blue-600 underline" target="_blank" href="%s">Code Snippets</a>.'=>'在此添加修改结账页面的 PHP 代码片段。如果您有大量代码片段，建议使用 <a class="text-blue-600 underline" target="_blank" href="%s">代码片段</a>。','Please omit the opening PHP tag.'=>'请省略开头的 PHP 标签。','Add custom JavaScript and PHP that runs on the checkout page.'=>'添加在结账页面运行的自定义 JavaScript 和 PHP。','Add custom JavaScript and PHP that runs on the Order Received / Thank You page.'=>'添加在订单接收/感谢页面运行的自定义 JavaScript 和 PHP。','Add custom JavaScript and PHP that runs on the Order Pay page.'=>'添加在订单支付页面运行的自定义 JavaScript 和 PHP。','Exclude From Abandoned Cart Recovery By Role'=>'按角色排除废弃购物车恢复','Check any user role that should be excluded from abandoned cart emails.'=>'勾选应排除在废弃购物车邮件之外的用户角色。','Are you sure you want to delete all tracked carts?'=>'您确定要删除所有跟踪的购物车吗？','Is equal to'=>'等于','Is not equal to'=>'不等于','Is greater than'=>'大于','Is less than'=>'小于','Is greater or equal to'=>'大于或等于','Is less than or equal to'=>'小于或等于','Was placed on'=>'下单于','Was not placed on'=>'未列入','Was placed after'=>'放置在后面','Was placed before'=>'放置在前面','On'=>'在','Not on'=>'不在','After'=>'之后','Before'=>'之前','At least one of the selected'=>'至少一个被选中','All of the selected'=>'所有被选中','None of the selected'=>'没有被选中','Select Condition…'=>'选择条件…','Select Order Type…'=>'选择订单类型…','Select Product Category…'=>'选择产品类别…','Select Product Tag…'=>'选择产品标签…','Select Product…'=>'选择产品…','Select Inventory Status…'=>'选择库存状态…','Select User Role…'=>'选择用户角色…','Cart Contents'=>'购物车内容','Is empty'=>'为空','Is not empty'=>'不为空','Contains (Products)'=>'包含（产品）','Contains (Categories)'=>'包含（类别）','Contains (Tags)'=>'包含（标签）','Cart Total Quantity'=>'购物车总数量','Cart Subtotal'=>'购物车小计','Quantity of Product in Cart'=>'购物车中产品数量','Quantity of Category in Cart'=>'购物车中类别数量','Cart Coupons'=>'购物车优惠券','Has no coupon'=>'无优惠券','Has coupon'=>'有优惠券','Enter coupon codes...'=>'输入优惠券代码…','Customer History: Total Spent'=>'客户历史：总消费','Customer History: Average Order Value'=>'客户历史：平均订单价值','Customer History: Total Orders'=>'客户历史：订单总数','Customer History: Quantity of Product Ordered'=>'客户历史：订购产品数量','Customer History: Quantity of Category Ordered'=>'客户历史：订购类别数量','Customer History: Time Since Order'=>'客户历史：距离订单时间','First order'=>'首次订单','Last order'=>'最后订单','Customer History: Time Since Product Ordered'=>'客户历史：距离产品订购时间','Customer History: Time Since Category Ordered'=>'客户历史：距离类别订购时间','Customer History: Date of Order'=>'客户历史：订单日期','Customer History: Date of Product Ordered'=>'客户历史：产品订购日期','First ordered'=>'首次订购','Last ordered'=>'最后订购','Customer History: Date of Category Ordered'=>'客户历史：类别订购日期','Product Inventory'=>'产品库存','Is in stock'=>'有库存','Is out of stock'=>'缺货','Is on backorder'=>'预订中','Quantity of Product in Stock'=>'库存中产品数量','Shipping Country'=>'运输国家','Billing Country'=>'账单国家','Add rule'=>'添加规则','Show If'=>'显示条件','And If'=>'并且条件','Delete Rule'=>'删除规则','woocommerceShipping'=>'配送','full stringSuffix'=>'后缀']];